Description: Write a program to check whether a number is even or odd.
Example:
Input: number = 4
Output: Even
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Solutions:
def even_odd(n):
  if(n%2==0):
    return "EVEN"
  else:
    return "ODD"

number=int(input("Enter the number you want to check:"))
result=even_odd(number)
print(result)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
